Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:16.12,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}是一个不听话的胆小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.78,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an2\fad(250,250)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.78,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fad(250,250)}I know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.49,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}とはいえ好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.49,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}话虽如此 但喜欢二字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.46,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}真顔じゃ困る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.46,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}一脸认真地说会很苦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.86,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}居心地いいキミの隣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.86,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an9\fad(250,250)}待在你身边就觉得很舒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:29.33,ed,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(250,250)}不器用すぎだねふたり
